<HEADLINE> Zambian, Rwandan Vice-Presidents Meet </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, December 21 (Xinhua) -- Zambian Vice-President
Christon Tembo said today that the relationship between Zambia
and Rwanda is becoming stronger and stronger, according to Zambia
News Agency ZANA.
</P>
<P>
