Reflecting the firmness, the BSE sensitive index began firm at
3553.68 and rallied smartly to the day's high of 3629.42 before
closing at 3616.34.
</P>
<P>
Bull operators have entered the market and enlarged their
commitments in the opening session to build up positions that were
likely to earn them good benefits in the next few days.  
