<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, December 22 (Xinhua) -- Michelle de Bruin, the triple
gold medalist in Atlanta Olympic Games, said she will skip the
World Swimming Championships next month in Australia because of
injury, reports reaching here said on Monday.
</P>
<P>
