</P>
<P>
The accident is the worst of its kind this year, police said.
Some of the dead were not recorded because relatives and friends
took the bodies away.
</P>
<P>
The cause of the accident is reckless driving, The New Vision
paper said. One of the drivers who caused the accident is said to
be trained only last week and was warned not to go a long
distance, the local English newspaper added in its report.
