<HEADLINE> Eritrea, Turkey Seal Trade Accord </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, December 22 (Xinhua) -- Eritrea and Turkey have
signed a general accord on promoting trade and technical
cooperation between them, the latest issue of weekly English
''Eritrea Profile'' reported.
