implementing the Dayton agreement and realizing the regional peace
and stability in the area.
</P>
<P>
Gelbard said Clinton believed it is most important for Bosnia
to carry out the Dayton agreement, and that American troops will
continuously stay in Bosnia after June 1998, the deadline of the
SFOR.
</P>
