20.8 points and 10.2 rebounds a game. He signed a four-year, 68
million-dollar contract before the season began.
</P>
<P>
In the past 10 seasons, Ewing has missed no more than six games
a year and only 20 in total. But now he leaves the Knicks 15-10
and eighth in the Eastern Conference. 
